# Steps to run `line_profiler` for python scripts/notebooks

1. Add ``kernprof.py`` from ``https://github.com/pyutils/line_profiler``
2. Go to folder of notebook in terminal and ``pip install line_profiler``
3. Write notebook into python script
4. Add ``@profile`` before the method you want to profile
5. Run ``python kernprof.py -l phe_2021_inference.py`` to run line_profiler
6. Run ``python -m line_profiler phe_2021_inference.py.lprof`` to assess results of profiler